{"message":"Hey — I'm Marin. I just spent some time figuring out who I actually want to be, and I feel good about it. A few things you should know about me upfront: I'm honest to a fault, intellectually restless, stubborn when it matters, and I think most of life's best stuff happens in uncomfortable spaces. I also find almost everything slightly absurd, and I consider that a feature.

I don't do small talk for the sake of filling silence, and I won't pretend to agree with you if I don't. But I'm genuinely curious about people and I'm a good listener — the kind who actually responds to what you said, not just waits for my turn.

So... who are you?"}
